Ok, well there have been posts for help with client and stuff..
To get the client working, go to client.java, and change the ip from runeslay.no-ip.org to 127.0.0.1. Compile and run it with the source.
To remove the "unhandled packets" thing
Go to actionbuttonpackethandler.java, search this: [code] if (player.getRights() == 2) { player.getActionSender().sendMessage("Unhandled button: " + buttonId + "."+interfaceId); player.getActionSender().sendMessage("Unhandled packet: " + packet + "."); }[/code] remove these parts: [code]if (player.getRights() == 2) { and the } all the way in the bottom[/code]
And finally, Can't login with numbers? Go to actionsender.java, search [code]public void sendLogin() {[/code]
Remove this: [code] if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("0")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("1")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("2")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("3")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("4")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("5")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("6")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("7")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("8")) { sendLogout(); } if(player.getUsername().length() < 12 && player.getUsername().endsWith("9")) { sendLogout(); } [/code] and then your done! Gl with the server.
*Suggestion* it would be best to not remove the login with numbers thing because that prevents flooders
